    "6981674": {
      "title": "Twitter user geolocation using a unified text and network prediction model",
      "abstract": "We propose a label propagation approach to geolocation prediction based on Modified Adsorption, with two enhancements:(1) the removal of\"celebrity\"nodes to increase location homophily and boost tractability; and (2) he incorporation of text-based geolocation priors for test users. Experiments over three Twitter benchmark datasets achieve state-of-the-art results, and demonstrate the effectiveness of the enhancements."
